The paper deals with natural language understanding and transfer learning, which are common topics in the sub-field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of pre-trained models and the proposed domain-adaptive pre-training strategy also suggest a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The task of entity linking involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and the use of language models to understand text (cs.NE).
